# ============================================================================
# Future Team Assignments (Template)
# ============================================================================
# When adding team members, use these patterns:
#
# ML/DL Experts:
#   papers/*/models/                @mvillmow @ml-expert
#   src/ml_odyssey/training/        @mvillmow @ml-expert
#
# Performance Engineers:
#   **/*simd*                       @mvillmow @perf-engineer
#   **/*benchmark*                  @mvillmow @perf-engineer
#
# Security Engineers:
#   **/*security*                   @mvillmow @security-engineer
#   **/*auth*                       @mvillmow @security-engineer
#
# Documentation Writers:
#   *.md                            @mvillmow @doc-writer
#   docs/                           @mvillmow @doc-writer
#
# DevOps Engineers:
#   .github/workflows/              @mvillmow @devops-engineer
#   pixi.toml                       @mvillmow @devops-engineer
#
# Research Scientists:
#   papers/*/theory/                @mvillmow @research-scientist
#   papers/*/experiments/           @mvillmow @research-scientist

# ============================================================================
# Order and Precedence Notes
# ============================================================================
# 1. Most specific patterns at the END of file override general patterns
# 2. Default owner (*) at top catches everything not matched below
# 3. Security patterns override domain patterns (placed near end)
# 4. File type patterns (*.mojo) catch files in any directory
#
# Testing CODEOWNERS:
#   gh api /repos/mvillmow/ProjectOdyssey/codeowners/errors
#
# Validating a PR:
#   gh pr view <number> --json reviewRequests
